{"word":"G1006 - βόσκω - bóskō - bos'-ko - Feed","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βόσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">bóskō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">bos'-ko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Feed</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மேய்ந்து கொண்டிரு, மேய்"},{"paragraph":"to feed"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A prolonged form of a primary verb (compare <a href=\"#/G977 - βιβρώσκω - bibrṓskō - bib-ro'-sko/977\">G977</a> and <a href=\"#/G1016 - βοῦς - boûs - booce/1016\">G1016</a>); to <i>pasture</i>; by extension to <i>fodder</i>; reflexively to <i>graze:</i> - feed, keep.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}